snippet.title: A Kiss For The Petals - Maidens of Michael PV [English Subtitles]
snippet.description:
Update 9 November 2012: Download an updated, higher-quality version at http://petalsgarden.axypb.net/2012/10/23/a-kiss-for-the-petals-maidens-of-michael-promotional-video/

This is a re-creation of the English subtitled promotional video for A Kiss For The Petals - Maidens of Michael (その花びらにくちづけを　ミカエルの乙女たち Sono Hanabira ni Kuchizuke wo - Michael no Otome-tachi) originally created by k01.

Translated by Ralen and k01
Typeset by k01 and AXYPB

Original video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ke4oKgCOB7o 
Original subtitles: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nIx_VX6XF0E

More information: http://petalsgarden.axypb.net/2012/07/21/yurin-yurin-official-website/
